Now, add the two base-10 results:

\[
33506 + 31845 = 65351
\]

Next, convert \(65351_{10}\) back to base-5. We do this by dividing \(65351\) by powers of 5 and recording the remainders:

\[
65351 \div 5 = 13070 \text{ remainder } 1
\]
\[
13070 \div 5 = 2614 \text{ remainder } 0
\]
\[
2614 \div 5 = 522 \text{ remainder } 4
\]
\[
522 \div 5 = 104 \text{ remainder } 2
\]
\[
104 \div 5 = 20 \text{ remainder } 4
\]
\[
20 \div 5 = 4 \text{ remainder } 0
\]
\[
4 \div 5 = 0 \text{ remainder } 4
\]

Reading the remainders from bottom to top, we get \(4004241_5\).

Therefore,
\[
2033011_5 + 2004340_5 = 4004241_5
\]
Summarized as:
\[
2033011_5 + 2004340_5 = 33506_{10} + 31845_{10} = 65351_{10} = 4004241_{5}
